pullRequest.body:
There are still some useless lemmas that were simply ported from `Algebra.Order.Monoid.Lemmas`, such as just chain an existing lemma with an assumption and lemmas whose assumptions imply `1 â‰¤ 0`. This PR removes them.

Also, some lemmas have both assumptions like `1 < a` `0 < a`. This PR uses `ZeroLEOneClass` to remove redundant assumptions.
